TY  - JOUR
T1  - Maximizing the Efficiency of the U.S. Liver Allocation System Through Region Design
AU  - Kong, Nan
AU  - Schaefer, Andrew J.
AU  - Hunsaker, Brady
AU  - Roberts, Mark S.
Y1  - 2010/10/29
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1249
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1249
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
