T1  - Imperfect Competition in Financial Markets: An Empirical Study of Island and Nasdaq
AU  - Biais, Bruno
AU  - Bisière, Christophe
AU  - Spatt, Chester
Y1  - 2010/12/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1243
