TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Behavior of Risk and Market Prices of Risk Over the Nasdaq Bubble Period
AU  - Bakshi, Gurdip
AU  - Wu, Liuren
Y1  - 2010/12/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1256
